# Local-only secrets. Copy to `.env` (which is git-ignored) and fill in.
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is used ONLY by the deliberate Lane 1 (local/manual) paid
# steps — Stage 3 extraction and Stage 4's synthesize sub-step. It must NEVER
# be added to GitHub Actions / CI (see build_spec.md cost guardrails): CI has
# no credential to bill with, so no bug or loop can spend money.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Hugging Face token for the deploy-to-Space step. Stored as a GitHub Actions
# secret (HF_TOKEN) for CI deploys, and locally here only if you deploy by hand.
HF_TOKEN=
